def FeX_OI_fit_func(wvl,int1,int2,int3,wvl1,wvl2,fwhm1,fwhm2,int_cont):
    return gaussian(wvl,wvl1,int1,fwhm1) + gaussian(wvl,wvl2,int2,fwhm2) + \
             + gaussian(wvl,wvl1+1028.157-1027.431,int3,fwhm1) + int_cont
